Alien status :—Neophyte native to the North America, it can be considered invasive in Italy . The first record in Europe was in 1806 for France (
Bátori et al. 2012
) and it is nowadays considered as naturalized in most European countries. First Italian record is in 1868 for MOL ( Thellung 1907 , Saccardo 1909 ).
